### Button
  Button component
  Import: `import { Button } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - variant: 'default' | 'flat' | 'stroked' | 'basic' | 'icon' (optional) — The variant of the button.
- 'default': Standard button with background color.
- 'flat': Button with no background color.
- 'stroked': Button with a border.
- 'basic': Minimal button with no styling.
- 'icon': Button intended for icon use.
    - size: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' (optional) — The size of the button.
- 'sm': Small button.
- 'md': Medium button.
- 'lg': Large button.
